  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 9-21-1 THROUGH 9-21-19, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH ESTABLISH THE ADMINISTRATIVE OFFICE OF COURTS, FOR POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 9-23-1 THROUGH 9-23-23, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH ENACT THE ALYCE GRIFFIN CLARKE INTERVENTION COURT ACT, FOR POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 9-23-51, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH ESTABLISHES THE DRUG COURT FUND IN THE STATE TREASURY, FOR POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 9-25-1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH CREATES THE VETERAN TREATMENT COURTS, FOR THE PURPOSE OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 9-27-1 THROUGH 9-27-21, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH ENACT THE RIVERS MCGRAW MENTAL HEALTH TREATMENT COURT ACT, FOR POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
